  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nIf we get a Goodbye on the behaviour then we should request all rpc handlers to disconnect. With that we shouldn't need to propagate the Goodbye message. After the handlers have disconnected, we should get a ConnectionClosed Swarm event and with that send a \"peer disconnected\" event to the network\r\n\r\nThis is locked because making the handlers disconnect gracefully is a work in progress.",
